item.title: CVE-2023-22298|2024-08-02T10:07:05.732Z -- pgadmin%20project -- pgadmin%204
item.description: Open redirect vulnerability in pgAdmin 4 versions prior to v6.14 allows a remote unauthenticated attacker to redirect a user to an arbitrary web site and conduct a phishing attack by having a user to access a specially crafted URL.
